1
00:00:38,194 --> 00:00:38,950
What are you doing here?

2
00:00:38,950 --> 00:00:39,960
What are you doing here?!

3
00:00:39,965 --> 00:00:43,268
Punk, it's an iron castle. 
 It's impenetrable.

4
00:00:43,268 --> 00:00:46,938
You're right! It's impossible. 
 Now, just give it up.

5
00:00:48,950 --> 00:00:52,150
Guys, on this earth... 
 there's no place that can't be stolen.

6
00:00:54,050 --> 00:00:56,050
I'm... Iljimae.

7
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:57,140
Step aside, step aside!

8
00:00:57,140 --> 00:00:58,810
Hey, step aside, step aside!

9
00:00:58,850 --> 00:00:59,850
Who it is?

10
00:01:00,350 --> 00:01:03,321
I'm the ice merchant here!

11
00:01:03,321 --> 00:01:06,424
If I don't go quickly, it will melt. 
    

12
00:01:06,424 --> 00:01:08,693
Move away. 
 Move away!

13
00:01:08,693 --> 00:01:09,827
Hey, what's that?!

14
00:01:09,827 --> 00:01:12,130
Easy! Take it easy!

15
00:01:16,936 --> 00:01:19,738
I've brought the ice for the feast!

16
00:01:20,989 --> 00:01:24,375
I've received the order to fill up the ice cave!

17
00:01:24,375 --> 00:01:28,780
We were ordered to restrict anyone from 
 coming in or out tonight.

18
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:30,315
You must wait until dawn.

19
00:01:30,315 --> 00:01:31,649
Until dawn?!

20
00:01:31,649 --> 00:01:33,584
No, no, there's no way!

21
00:01:33,584 --> 00:01:37,088
I'm not an expert, 
 but the ice will all melt for sure.

22
00:01:37,088 --> 00:01:39,290
Really...

23
00:01:39,290 --> 00:01:42,793
What a waste... I ran all the way from Seobinggo 
 without even stopping for a minute.

24
00:01:43,695 --> 00:01:44,662
Wait!

25
00:01:44,662 --> 00:01:45,730
Yes, Sir.

26
00:01:50,135 --> 00:01:52,135
By the way, is there anything important?

27
00:01:52,135 --> 00:01:53,305
It's an emergency...

28
00:01:53,305 --> 00:01:56,140
We heard Iljimae will be robbing this place tonight.

29
00:01:56,140 --> 00:02:00,812
Why is this ice block so red?

30
00:02:00,812 --> 00:02:04,382
That's Raspberry (Korean Mountain Berries) wine that's been frozen the entire winter on the bank of Daedong river.

31
00:02:04,450 --> 00:02:09,150
It is a specially frozen wine to welcome the Ching's ambassadors during the feast for tomorrow.

32
00:02:12,454 --> 00:02:15,226
It's true. it's Raspberry wine.

33
00:02:15,226 --> 00:02:16,927
There's nothing else here, sir!

34
00:02:20,431 --> 00:02:21,833
Let him in!

35
00:02:21,833 --> 00:02:23,234
Yes sir!

36
00:02:23,234 --> 00:02:25,203
Thank you. Take care.

37
00:06:07,391 --> 00:06:08,293
Is everything okay?

38
00:06:08,293 --> 00:06:12,129
Yes sir! We are on guard. 
 Even a mouse cannot pass by unnoticed.

39
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:42,250
What is going on?

40
00:08:43,313 --> 00:08:46,984
Close the door! Light a fire! Light!

41
00:09:12,075 --> 00:09:14,412
Everyone!  Light the fire!

42
00:09:21,386 --> 00:09:23,855
Go after him!  He couldn't have gone too far yet!

43
00:09:23,855 --> 00:09:24,789
Yes, sir!

44
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,894
Over here!

45
00:09:57,589 --> 00:09:58,423
Good job, soldier.

46
00:10:03,593 --> 00:10:06,231
Iljimae, you're a dead man.

47
00:10:06,231 --> 00:10:10,169
You're the notorious Iljimae. 
 Let's take a look at your face.

48
00:10:10,950 --> 00:10:11,650
Soldier!

49
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:12,350
Yes, sir!

50
00:10:24,348 --> 00:10:27,352
That bastard.....That bastard was Iljimae!

51
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:42,950
No!

52
00:11:00,218 --> 00:11:04,322
See? Like I said, there's nothing on this earth 
 that I can't steal.... I AM Iljimae!

53
00:11:04,322 --> 00:11:06,190
Since I'm Iljimae.

54
00:11:09,864 --> 00:11:11,232
It's Iljimae!

55
00:11:11,232 --> 00:11:13,268
Capture him!

56
00:12:22,204 --> 00:12:24,205
Gyeom.

57
00:12:24,205 --> 00:12:29,177
There are many types of pretty flowers, 
 but why do you only like plum blossoms?

58
00:12:29,177 --> 00:12:32,180
Though it resembles cherry blossom, it's not as pretencious,

59
00:12:32,180 --> 00:12:39,751
Though it resembles pear blossoms, it's not as pitiful. 
 That's why I'm fond of the plum.

60
00:12:39,751 --> 00:12:45,126
The plum holds the fragrance of a noble scholar. 
 There's no other flower beautiful than plum blossom in my eyes.

61
00:13:21,896 --> 00:13:24,098
Do you truly see it?

62
00:13:24,098 --> 00:13:30,338
Yes, I see a bright red color with very gallant energy.

63
00:13:30,338 --> 00:13:32,807
How can you see that?

64
00:13:32,807 --> 00:13:38,012
Shortly after I was born, I have lost my vision due to a fever.

65
00:13:38,012 --> 00:13:40,848
But afterwards, I gained another pair of eyes.

66
00:13:40,848 --> 00:13:44,651
I can see those things that  other people can't see.

67
00:13:44,651 --> 00:13:52,393
In my eyes, I can see the strong energy of the sun 
 who will receive all the respect of the people.

68
00:13:57,565 --> 00:14:00,802
He saw the things that shouldn't have been seen.

69
00:14:00,802 --> 00:14:04,272
Likewise, I heard things that shouldn't have been heard.

70
00:14:10,979 --> 00:14:12,614
Who else knows about this?

71
00:14:12,614 --> 00:14:17,885
I... won't tell anyone else about...

72
00:15:04,933 --> 00:15:09,304
If you feel stuffy, why don't you go out for a stroll?

73
00:15:09,304 --> 00:15:13,340
Now that you mention it, within the next few days 
 I plan to go to Hanyang.

74
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:16,076
Sir Shim Ji Won wishes to see me.

75
00:15:16,076 --> 00:15:19,981
Father! Please look at this drawing!

76
00:15:19,981 --> 00:15:22,883
Gyeom, is this your drawing?

77
00:15:22,883 --> 00:15:23,985
Yes.

78
00:15:23,985 --> 00:15:26,854
I feel ashamed now.....

79
00:15:26,854 --> 00:15:32,058
Dear, isn't his skills better than me?

80
00:15:32,058 --> 00:15:35,463
My dear Gyeom, you deserve a reward.

81
00:15:35,463 --> 00:15:36,965
What shall I give you?

82
00:15:36,965 --> 00:15:41,500
How about your favorite beef jerky?

83
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,871
Then what would you like?

84
00:15:43,871 --> 00:15:48,276
Mother, please allow me to accompany Father to Hanyang.

85
00:15:48,276 --> 00:15:54,146
That is not an impossible wish, okay.

86
00:15:54,146 --> 00:15:59,717
Huh? It's the Whistling bird!

87
00:15:59,717 --> 00:16:05,693
Seeing that the whistling bird is here, 
 it is definitely spring now.

88
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,441
Shoot!

89
