We couldn't find that blind man's wife.

90
00:17:16,464 --> 00:17:20,801
I think she found out and ran off already.

91
00:17:20,801 --> 00:17:21,569
Let's go!

92
00:17:37,319 --> 00:17:38,086
Stop crying!

93
00:17:42,256 --> 00:17:44,025
Soo Mak, go ahead and run in that direction!

94
00:17:44,025 --> 00:17:45,627
Remember never to look back....Just run!!!

95
00:17:45,627 --> 00:17:46,761
Mother!

96
00:17:46,761 --> 00:17:51,565
You must never tell anyone that your father 
 was a blind fortune teller, understand?

97
00:17:51,565 --> 00:17:53,734
Mother!

98
00:17:53,734 --> 00:18:01,438
Soo Mak, you are a brother.

99
00:18:01,438 --> 00:18:03,377
You must take good care of Soon (sister name).

100
00:18:16,390 --> 00:18:18,025
Quick!

101
