It is white powder sugar.

161
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:09,625
Sugar?

162
00:25:09,625 --> 00:25:14,039
Wow, it's sweet and melts in my mouth.

163
00:25:14,709 --> 00:25:18,088
Damm....Those Aristocrats' mouth must feel good.....

164
00:25:18,088 --> 00:25:21,301
They shove this in their mouths all day and night.

165
00:25:21,301 --> 00:25:25,283
You are pretty chatty?

166
00:25:25,925 --> 00:25:30,091
I need to open that box, so hurry 
 and bring me something to open it with.

167
00:25:30,091 --> 00:25:31,715
Sure, go ahead and look all you want!

168
00:25:31,715 --> 00:25:33,740
They are all government authorized merchandises.

169
00:25:33,740 --> 00:25:35,902
Quickly!

170
00:25:42,618 --> 00:25:46,957
I am really lucky today.

171
00:25:46,957 --> 00:25:49,864
How much money would each of these fetch?

172
00:25:49,864 --> 00:25:54,033
Let me see, I gotta take this for my Cha Dol to eat.

173
00:26:00,772 --> 00:26:04,797
Shit!!! Where are all these soldiers coming from?

174
00:26:04,797 --> 00:26:05,940
Here it is.

175
00:26:05,940 --> 00:26:11,173
Go ahead and open it.

176
00:26:11,173 --> 00:26:15,654
My lord, there was someone else 
 to inspect us earlier. Why do you come again?

177
00:26:15,654 --> 00:26:16,315
What are you talking about?

178
00:26:16,315 --> 00:26:18,666
The other person...

179
00:26:18,666 --> 00:26:23,920
That person

180
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:28,370
Oh, no....that thief!! That thief!!!

181
00:26:35,176 --> 00:26:38,587
Where has he gone off

182
00:26:38,587 --> 00:26:43,185
Has he gone to heaven?

183
00:26:43,185 --> 00:26:47,793
Oh! What the?!

184
00:27:02,969 --> 00:27:06,444
Please believe me.....My father is really not a thief!!!

185
00:27:06,444 --> 00:27:08,639
Don't waste my time, hurry up and follow me!

186
00:27:24,650 --> 00:27:26,794
Oh my god, here you are!

187
00:27:26,794 --> 00:27:30,176
I heard that Cha Dol has got into trouble at the market.

188
00:27:30,176 --> 00:27:31,339
What do you mean trouble?

189
00:27:31,339 --> 00:27:33,246
I am telling you....It is not me!!!

190
00:27:40,953 --> 00:27:43,930
Wait!

191
00:27:48,572 --> 00:27:49,799
What's the matter, young master?

192
00:27:49,799 --> 00:27:52,277
Let me see his hands.

193
00:27:52,277 --> 00:27:53,987
Pardon?

194
00:27:53,987 --> 00:27:56,991
Young master, why would you want to see his hand?

195
00:28:07,069 --> 00:28:09,034
Just look at this.

196
00:28:09,034 --> 00:28:11,704
See? There are trace of white powder here....

197
00:28:11,704 --> 00:28:13,452
What could it be?

198
00:28:13,452 --> 00:28:15,408
I'm not sure.

199
00:28:15,408 --> 00:28:17,001
Here, taste it.

200
00:28:19,613 --> 00:28:22,800
It tastes kind of sweet.

201
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:25,334
This is the white powder that's on dried persimmons.

202
00:28:25,334 --> 00:28:30,297
When you sun-dry a persimmon, the sugar seeps out 
 and dries into a white powder coating.

203
00:28:30,297 --> 00:28:34,085
Oh, so that is why it tastes sweet.

204
00:28:34,085 --> 00:28:39,726
Father, may I see your hands, please?

205
00:28:39,726 --> 00:28:41,008
Here, look.

206
00:28:41,008 --> 00:28:43,515
On my father's hands, too, there's no such white powder.

207
00:28:43,515 --> 00:28:49,426
On his hand too, no white powder. My father's hands as well!

208
00:28:49,426 --> 00:28:51,057
Then how could there be 
 this white powder on the ornament?

209
00:28:51,057 --> 00:28:54,591
I can't be sure.

210
00:28:54,591 --> 00:28:57,452
Tell that Young Master to show his hands.

211
00:28:57,452 --> 00:28:59,215
Pardon?

212
00:29:10,513 --> 00:29:14,062
Seize him!

213
00:29:14,062 --> 00:29:16,077
Gyeom, how did you...

214
00:29:16,077 --> 00:29:17,762
It's nothing.

215
00:29:17,762 --> 00:29:21,314
Earlier I just saw the young master eating a dried persimmon.

216
00:29:21,314 --> 00:29:26,382
You guys should let go of this innocent kid right away.

217
00:29:26,382 --> 00:29:28,211
Yes, my lord.

218
00:29:33,279 --> 00:29:35,316
Young master, thank you so much.

219
00:29:35,316 --> 00:29:36,805
Could I ask what is young master's name...

220
00:29:36,805 --> 00:29:38,921
My name is Gyeom. Lee Gyeom.

221
00:29:38,921 --> 00:29:40,763
And your name, my lord?

222
00:29:40,763 --> 00:29:44,121
Mine?

223
00:29:44,121 --> 00:29:46,717
My name is Lee Won Ho.

224
00:29:46,717 --> 00:29:49,379
I definitely will repay your kindness.

225
00:29:49,379 --> 00:29:51,120
Don't mention it.

226
00:29:51,120 --> 00:29:55,457
Just grow into a righteous and precious man. 
 That is all I ask.

227
00:29:55,457 --> 00:29:57,284
Isn't that right, Gyeom?

228
00:29:57,284 --> 00:29:58,082
Yes, Father.

229
00:29:58,082 --> 00:30:02,374
No, it's not enough. I will definitely repay you.

230
00:30:02,374 --> 00:30:04,093
Cha Dol!

231
00:30:04,093 --> 00:30:06,331
Mother!

232
00:30:06,331 --> 00:30:08,656
What has happened?

233
00:30:08,656 --> 00:30:09,885
Are you okay?

234
00:30:09,885 --> 00:30:12,201
It is that lord and the young master who rescued me.

235
00:30:19,202 --> 00:30:23,192
Is he your son?

236
00:30:25,449 --> 00:30:27,352
Let's go, Cha Dol.

237
00:30:59,422 --> 00:31:04,490
Mother, what's wrong?

238
00:31:04,490 --> 00:31:10,480
It's nothing. I just got dizzy, that's all.

239
00:31:25,327 --> 00:31:26,928
Is the food alright?

240
00:31:26,928 --> 00:31:28,964
Yes sir, it is really tasty.

241
00:31:28,964 --> 00:31:30,565
You are a good boy.

242
00:31:30,565 --> 00:31:35,269
I thought you would be a picky eater 
 but you eat this kind of food well...

243
00:31:35,269 --> 00:31:39,039
My lord!

244
00:31:39,039 --> 00:31:43,311
Why would you protect the child of such a lowly thief?

245
00:31:43,311 --> 00:31:45,714
Did you follow us here because you are still mad about that?

246
00:31:45,714 --> 00:31:50,618
It is because of people like you, my lord, 
 that the order of nobles and commoners is shaken.

247
00:31:50,650 --> 00:31:52,450
The order of nobles and commoners?

248
00:31:54,850 --> 00:31:59,950
Young master, When the noble acts nobly, 
 then he can truly be a noble.

249
00:31:59,994 --> 00:32:04,297
That is how you truly maintain public discipline.

250
00:32:04,297 --> 00:32:09,838
