My lord! My lord! Help me! I'll do it. I'll bury it.

507
00:58:29,653 --> 00:58:34,126
Will you?

508
00:58:34,126 --> 00:58:37,164
Let him go!

509
00:58:44,401 --> 00:58:48,372
Oh, oh...

510
00:58:48,372 --> 00:58:53,943
My arm, I can't move it at all.

511
00:58:53,943 --> 00:58:57,014
His arm seems to be out of joint.

512
00:58:57,014 --> 00:59:00,417
If so, he won't be able to climb up the wall anymore.

513
00:59:00,417 --> 00:59:03,120
Then... could you let me go...

514
00:59:03,120 --> 00:59:05,288
and my son as well....

515
00:59:08,291 --> 00:59:10,929
Though, I can't let you go.

516
00:59:10,929 --> 00:59:17,601
You have already seen the content of the letter. I'll be in trouble if you tell everyone.

517
00:59:17,601 --> 00:59:19,870
No, I won't tell anybody.

518
00:59:19,870 --> 00:59:22,205
I'll keep my mouth shut like a clam.

519
00:59:25,743 --> 00:59:29,012
Don't kill him, I'll do it for him.

520
00:59:29,012 --> 00:59:33,849
I'll do it for him. I beg you please spare my father's life. I'll do it for him.

521
00:59:42,397 --> 00:59:47,521
If you are spotted, your father will be dead immediately.

522
00:59:47,521 --> 00:59:54,961
Remember it, your father's life is in your hands.

523
01:00:32,932 --> 01:00:34,567
Hey!

524
01:00:34,567 --> 01:00:36,602
Uh...

525
01:00:36,602 --> 01:00:38,404
Hey, who are you?

526
01:00:38,404 --> 01:00:40,172
What are you doing here?

527
01:00:52,952 --> 01:00:54,220
My lord

528
01:00:54,220 --> 01:00:55,254
How was it?

529
01:00:55,254 --> 01:00:57,256
He made it.

530
01:01:01,227 --> 01:01:02,762
Where's the boy?

531
01:01:02,762 --> 01:01:05,965
He was prisoned together with his father.

532
01:01:07,733 --> 01:01:12,572
Finish both of them while everyone is sleeping.

533
01:01:12,572 --> 01:01:14,340
What?

534
01:01:14,340 --> 01:01:17,877
He is a little boy. Do you think that his mouth is trustworthy?

535
01:01:17,877 --> 01:01:21,347
If he spreads it around, everything will be over.

536
01:01:23,082 --> 01:01:26,786
Sister!  Sister!

537
01:01:28,621 --> 01:01:30,757
Why are you here this late?

538
01:01:30,757 --> 01:01:32,158
A major problem

539
01:01:32,158 --> 01:01:36,162
Swe Dol and Ja Dol are about to lose their lives.

540
01:01:40,632 --> 01:01:42,068
Swe Dol....!

541
01:01:58,718 --> 01:02:04,257
Please spare their lives, my lord.

542
01:02:04,257 --> 01:02:08,127
Why is it so noisy outside?

543
01:02:08,127 --> 01:02:13,831
My lord, please spare their lives, please.

544
01:02:13,831 --> 01:02:15,468
Who is she?

545
01:02:15,468 --> 01:02:21,071
Is she that thief's wife?

546
01:02:21,071 --> 01:02:25,111
How miserable you guys are!

547
01:02:32,986 --> 01:02:39,993
You.....You are.......Hold on, is that little boy your son?

548
01:02:39,993 --> 01:02:46,832
I beg you, my lord. Please spare my son and my husband.

549
01:02:46,832 --> 01:02:51,437
You're so unfortunate.

550
01:02:51,437 --> 01:02:55,207
How could you be a thief's wife?

551
01:02:57,594 --> 01:03:01,514
Your husband was caught climbing the walls of my house.

552
01:03:01,514 --> 01:03:05,517
Don't be so troublesome and return home now.

553
01:03:05,517 --> 01:03:07,286
That little boy...

554
01:03:13,192 --> 01:03:16,662
Do you really not know who the boy is, my lord?

555
01:03:28,174 --> 01:03:30,343
What?

556
01:03:30,343 --> 01:03:32,778
What are you saying?

557
01:03:32,778 --> 01:03:34,413
Say it again.

558
01:03:34,413 --> 01:03:37,115
Have you forgotten it, my lord?

559
01:03:37,115 --> 01:03:43,823
10 years ago, at that night...

560
01:03:43,823 --> 01:03:47,058
Of course I haven't.

561
01:03:47,058 --> 01:03:51,230
So?....then...?

562
01:03:51,230 --> 01:03:56,818
Do you really want to kill your son, my lord?

563
01:04:02,819 --> 01:04:07,022
Wh..wh... what are you doing now?

564
01:04:07,022 --> 01:04:15,454
Didn't you like me, when you came to my master's house, my lord?

565
01:04:15,454 --> 01:04:16,307
What?

566
01:04:16,307 --> 01:04:23,881
Didn't you tell my young master that you want to make me your concubine?

567
01:04:23,881 --> 01:04:28,893
That, that, that was... that's because...

568
01:04:28,893 --> 01:04:31,431
Please make me your concubine, my lord.

569
01:04:34,432 --> 01:04:38,014
I'll serve you.

570
01:05:13,775 --> 01:05:19,574
  Young Master, do you see? 

571
01:05:19,574 --> 01:05:27,307
  What I'm doing when I'm pregnant with your child? 

572
01:05:31,195 --> 01:05:33,184
I'm not going.

573
01:05:33,184 --> 01:05:35,901
I don't want to go.

574
01:05:35,901 --> 01:05:41,256
I want to live with father and mother.

575
01:05:46,068 --> 01:05:48,114
Remember!

576
01:05:48,114 --> 01:05:51,313
There is a royal blood running throughout your body

577
01:05:51,313 --> 01:05:55,071
Is it true that I'm a son of that lord?

578
01:05:55,071 --> 01:05:59,478
Yes, you are. You are the son of Lord Byun Shik.

579
01:05:59,478 --> 01:06:02,781
Therefore, you must stop playing with those underprivileged kids.

580
01:06:02,781 --> 01:06:07,074
If you run into me on the street one day, don't call me your mother either.

581
01:06:07,074 --> 01:06:09,859
Mother!

582
01:06:09,859 --> 01:06:13,647
You must grow up to be a noble man.

583
01:06:13,647 --> 01:06:16,863
You must be a righteous man.

584
01:06:16,863 --> 01:06:19,473
You got it?

585
01:06:39,065 --> 01:06:44,081
After he knew that you are not his biological son, he said he didn't want to see you again.

586
01:06:52,988 --> 01:06:56,646
This is a good enough.

587
01:06:56,646 --> 01:07:02,784
It would better for you to be a young master over there than to grow up with a father who is a thief.

588
01:07:02,784 --> 01:07:08,662
Ja Dol

589
01:07:13,126 --> 01:07:16,237
I can see you!

590
01:07:16,237 --> 01:07:18,811
I can see you from here!

591
01:07:18,811 --> 01:07:22,324
Ja Dol!

592
01:07:22,324 --> 01:07:29,220
I'm sorry, Ja Dol!

593
01:07:31,856 --> 01:07:39,800
Ja Dol...

594
01:07:44,023 --> 01:07:46,345
You must have been really scared, right Yeon?

595
01:07:46,345 --> 01:07:49,161
I'm ok, mother.

596
01:07:49,161 --> 01:07:54,156
We lost nothing in our house. I don't know what he came here for?

597
01:07:54,156 --> 01:07:58,988
Recently, I heard that many kids have become beggars in the street.

598
01:07:58,988 --> 01:08:02,293
I guess he came here to fill his tummy.

599
01:08:02,293 --> 01:08:05,528
I already ordered the servants to block his escaping path.

600
01:08:05,528 --> 01:08:07,509
You did a good job, my lady.

601
01:08:07,509 --> 01:08:11,266
If he dares to come here again, I won't let him go easily.

602
01:08:12,687 --> 01:08:16,164
Father, please teach me swordplay.

603
01:08:16,164 --> 01:08:17,118
Swordplay?

604
01:08:17,118 --> 01:08:22,185
Yes, father. So I can protect my family from thieves.

605
01:08:31,103 --> 01:08:35,125
Look at you now! How will you be able to catch thieves?

606
01:08:35,125 --> 01:08:37,624
How will you be able to protect your family?

607
01:08:56,698 --> 01:09:00,732
Losing alertness in front of a sword means death.

608
01:09:00,732 --> 01:09:03,537
Mother!

609
01:09:07,795 --> 01:09:11,322
If it was a real sword, father was already stabbed to death.

610
01:09:11,322 --> 01:09:14,195
Haha, what a despicable boy!

611
01:09:14,195 --> 01:09:19,080
I just learned that losing alertness in front of a sword means death.

612
01:09:19,080 --> 01:09:22,763
Ok, I admit it. I have lost to you.

613
01:09:26,622 --> 01:09:31,122
Geom, what do you think a sword means?

614
01:09:31,122 --> 01:09:32,664
Yes, father?

615
01:09:32,664 --> 01:09:35,119
There are two types of swords

616
01:09:35,119 --> 01:09:38,332
The one is for killing people

617
01:09:38,332 --> 01:09:43,045
On the contrary, the other one is for saving people.

618
01:09:43,045 --> 01:09:48,180
I hope you won't have to draw a sword for your entire life

619
01:09:48,180 --> 01:09:51,263
But if all else failed and you have to draw a sword,

620
01:09:51,263 --> 01:09:56,566
It should be a sword for the world and for the people.

621
01:09:56,566 --> 01:09:58,133
You got it?

622
01:09:58,133 --> 01:09:59,753
Yes, I do.

623
01:10:04,272 --> 01:10:07,159
My son is an adult now.

624
01:10:07,159 --> 01:10:12,213
We'll be counting on our Gyum. I can sleep in peace now.

625
01:10:17,551 --> 01:10:24,579
My lady! I suddenly feel like this year the titis are uniquely beautiful.

626
01:10:24,579 --> 01:10:29,976
I feel as if this is scenery that I won't be able to see ever again.

627
01:12:00,961 --> 01:12:01,624
Father!

628
01:12:01,624 --> 01:12:05,219
Geom, stay quiet in there and don't move!

629
01:12:05,219 --> 01:12:07,361
And don't even breathe heavily.

630
01:12:07,361 --> 01:12:11,859
Father!

631
01:12:11,859 --> 01:12:15,694
This thing is used to chase devils away.

632
01:12:15,694 --> 01:12:20,975
It'll protect you.

633
01:12:20,975 --> 01:12:25,873
Geom, no matter of whatever happens to me,

634
01:12:25,873 --> 01:12:27,877
You must survive.

635
01:12:27,877 --> 01:12:28,704
Father!

636
01:12:28,704 --> 01:12:30,145
Promise me!

637
01:12:30,145 --> 01:12:32,056
that you will be sure to survive.

638
01:12:32,056 --> 01:12:34,371
Yes, I will father!

639
01:12:48,069 --> 01:12:50,802
Father! Father! Father!

